{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Soulbound Dream\u00a0is an action game blending rogue-lite and puzzle elements. Explore dreams and nightmares to restore balance to Etherea. Use your emotions to modify your spells, defeat monsters, level up, and enhance your skills. Traverse these dreamlike worlds to unlock new spells and overcome the challenges that await </strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/story_title_en.png?t=1728928652\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/emotionnal_rings.png?t=1728928652\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Etherea was once a world of perfect balance, where dreams and nightmares coexisted in harmony, maintained by the Etherions, spiritual creatures bound to emotions. However, a mysterious force shattered this balance, strengthening the nightmares and plunging the world into chaos. The Guardians of Etherea, protectors of the realm, embarked on a desperate quest to understand and reverse this corruption. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Thane, a young guardian determined to restore balance by finding the legendary Balance of Etherea. Master your emotions to free lost souls and combat the darkness that is engulfing this once serene world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/Emotions_System_en.png?t=1728928652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Unlock and master up to 8 unique emotions (4 available in the demo)! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/emotionnal_switch_640_360_alpha_medians_256.gif?t=1728928652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Each emotion changes your skills and combat style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/skill_combo_640_360_alpha_medians_256.gif?t=1728928652\" />\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Progress through trials to find the Balance of Etherea!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/challenge1.gif?t=1728928652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Obtain new skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/tornade_640_360_alpha_medians_256.gif?t=1728928652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Fight corrupted entities to level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/fight_640_360_alpha_medians_256_short.gif?t=1728928652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Upgrade your character and their emotional skills as you level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/skill_upgrade_